\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {A1}{\ignorespaces 10-year return level of daily precipitation of the AROME model (first row), Météo-France stations (second row), and the AROME--Station difference (third row), with the spatial correlation between the stations and their closest grid points ($r$), the bias ($ME$) and the number of stations compared (n). The statistics are derived from daily data from 1959 to 2022. The contour lines show the 400 and 800 m isolines. To ease visualization, colour scales are symmetrically saturated above the 99th percentile.}}{28}{figure.caption.16}\protected@file@percent }
